*.pyc
tests/
conftest.py
.git/
.env
*.md
.gitignore          ← git config, not needed in container
.github/            ← CI workflows, not needed in container
*.yml               ← careful — only if no yml needed in app
Dockerfile          ← no need to copy itself into the image
Dockerfile*         ← covers Dockerfile.dev etc